form.official-title: To designate the facility of the United States Postal Service located at 103 Center Street West in Eatonville, Washington, as the National Park Ranger Margaret Anderson Post Office.

section.header: National Park Ranger Margaret Anderson Post Office

subsection.text: The facility of the United States Postal Service located at 103 Center Street West in Eatonville, Washington, shall be known and designated as the National Park Ranger Margaret Anderson Post Office.

Any reference in a law, map, regulation, document, paper, or other record of the United States to the facility referred to in subsection (a) shall be deemed to be a reference to the National Park Ranger Margaret Anderson Post Office.

attestation-group.attestation-date: Passed the House of Representatives March 24, 2014.
